{"tid":1128660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【左到癡哂線】13名市長聯署　促政府設立更多收容所接收難民","createTime":"2019-04-28T03:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T12:50:32.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4db33d02d7dd25e884f63f1136e45f54bfcb0fa5","tid":1128660,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"13名市長聯署 促政府設立更多收容所接收難民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/photo/bkn-20190428110055046-0428_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190428110357\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190428110055046-0428_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190428110357&h=53d2eb91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲難民潮持續，大量非法移民在街頭搭建帳幕聚居，嚴重影響社區民生和衞生。以法國巴黎市長伊達爾戈為首的13名市長，上周三（23日）向政府發出公開信，要求當局為政治庇護申請人提供更多收容所。<br />\n<br />\n公開信指，國內主要大城市正面對難民湧入問題，在人道上他們處於困境，對區內社會也造成騷擾。由於政府收容中心位置有限，非法移民往往在街角搭帳幕聚居。目前在巴黎北面城邊，已有1400名難民住在帳幕。<br />\n<br />\n有組織統計，只有一半難民可暫住在政府收容所。有援助組織表示，希望在未來4年為難民找到4萬個新床位。根據難民局統計，去年在法國政治庇護申請人多達122743，增加了22%。<br />\n<br />\n駐法國記者呂靜儀報道 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/mobile/bkn-20190428110055046-0428_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190428%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190428110055046-0428_00912_001.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a3226a68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/mobile/bkn-20190428110055046-0428_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"75b016682bc5662d38803914dda8fc8e39459cc2","tid":1128660,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"去年收逾12萬政庇申請 阿富汗人佔最多<br />\n<br />\n法國去年超過12.3萬人申請政治庇護，與前一年相比增加了22.7%，最多的申請者來自阿富汗。當局共批准4.6萬人的申請。<br />\n<br />\n阿富汗人佔最多，達1.03萬個申請，與2017年相比上升了55%。2018年在阿富汗有最多平民被殺害，有3804人喪生與極端回教組織塔利班和伊斯蘭國（IS）活動有關。<br />\n<br />\n2017年政庇申請人最多來自阿爾巴尼亞，在2018年數量下降27.6%，共有9683申請人。格魯吉亞申請人則大幅增加，去年共有7005人，增幅為256%。敍利亞申請人數量下降了2成，蘇丹申請人數量則減少5%。<br />\n<br />\n去年政庇首次申請人，包括有成年人陪同的未成年人士，數量升至114226。另有9399人申請重新審核或重開檔案。<br />\n<br />\n駐法國記者呂靜儀報道 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/mobile/bkn-20190428030457979-0428_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190428%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190428030457979-0428_00912_001.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=077c848a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/mobile/bkn-20190428030457979-0428_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3ab2c3aa87f5bfa604af211224b54a7e021f0f4b","tid":1128660,"uid":54337,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"法蘭西不如改名啦。而家叫法蘭西斯坦算啦"},{"pid":"87c9d4ffa030dd79c72787f534824b46610182d9","tid":1128660,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"就黎恐襲變週年活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a511e131354a4e0b51ca638af65d6a6346910991","tid":1128660,"uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:28:16.000Z","msg":"少女光天化日在火車上遭強姦 周圍無人舉報<br />\n<br />\n法國南部艾斯普羅旺斯地區一名15歲少女，本月中乘搭火車時，竟於光天化日下在車上遭強姦，據報雖然當時列車上有巡警，周圍也有其他乘客，但卻無人舉報。少女翌日報警，最後警方拘捕一名疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n事發於17日下午，受害人在當地一列跨區火車上遭人強姦，她當時的車程只有14分鐘。期間火車上有巡邏警員，也有報道指她出事位置周圍有其他乘客，但無人舉報。<br />\n<br />\n受害人翌日與家人報警。一名28歲男子隨後在馬賽被捕。警方利用車站監察系統的片段和交通卡記錄鎖定該疑犯。鐵路公司內部也就事件展開調查，形容罪行「可怕」。它表示當時火車上有3名警員，但不在罪行發生的車卡。<br />\n<br />\n據統計在2017至2018年之間，有關馬賽-艾斯普羅旺斯行車線的罪案舉報數量下降了超過4成。鐵路公司計劃重組監察人員工作，以確保乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n駐法國記者呂靜儀報道 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/mobile/bkn-20190428060100093-0428_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190428%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190428060100093-0428_00912_001.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=0bd86fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190428/mobile/bkn-20190428060100093-0428_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無講人種<br />\n無講國籍<br />\n無種膚色<br />\n大家自己估 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdccdf288b454cb3b237598a08e3a274a142275","tid":1128660,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"法國玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a358f326d1f7a9153bd6ef196f5b6849a84dbb1","tid":1128660,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"d歐洲既精英最後會比人迫走哂去美國, 然後美國就會好似world war z咁起牆, d難民攻入黎直接用火燒<br />\n左膠大愛撚沒路"},{"pid":"dd8e3a433721624f2cb9f48fb0cafee52c85b6bf","tid":1128660,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a358f326d1f7a9153bd6ef196f5b6849a84dbb1","tid":1128660,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"d歐洲既精英最後會比人迫走哂去美國, 然後美國就會好似world war z咁起牆, d難民攻入黎直接用火燒<br />\n左膠大愛撚沒路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"歐洲一早沉撚左淪<br />\n得返波蘭..俄佬果堆"},{"pid":"55106f98cb1d1639407603d88dfb434efb62fdf4","tid":1128660,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c74ca1d0527153354f41ab11a2e22403ed06eec","tid":1128660,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"全部驅逐啦仲收,傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42312f1479be8d89eb1f4c7875f6bf9929293c82","tid":1128660,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:45:41.000Z","msg":"大愛左狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230719f30c1b8a54df3f31778d75802a6507a08b","tid":1128660,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"香港報紙（唔計SCMP）除咗中台之外，幾時開始有人駐外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4238b9df3beb811a4beb95307168b25500d1eb","tid":1128660,"uid":51717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"學侵侵咁樣，班市長咁鐘意收容，就係佢哋個市長嘅屋企同班有錢佬豪宅附近起開放式收容所，俾班&ldquo;難民&rdquo;自由出入居住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779d46ffacfe9680eb5b91433165a4d60c5e0a5b","tid":1128660,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"230719f30c1b8a54df3f31778d75802a6507a08b","tid":1128660,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"香港報紙（唔計SCMP）除咗中台之外，幾時開始有人駐外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"細個做留學生賣字試過俾報社叫駐美記者"},{"pid":"4e9a10f88ec7efe94708710c6415a51155b1e74e","tid":1128660,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779d46ffacfe9680eb5b91433165a4d60c5e0a5b","tid":1128660,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"230719f30c1b8a54df3f31778d75802a6507a08b","tid":1128660,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"香港報紙（唔計SCMP）除咗中台之外，幾時開始有人駐外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"細個做留學生賣字試過俾報社叫駐美記者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"間報館咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5540b47cda76345a1f2a2a80c85b3db2d16caddf","tid":1128660,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e9a10f88ec7efe94708710c6415a51155b1e74e","tid":1128660,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779d46ffacfe9680eb5b91433165a4d60c5e0a5b","tid":1128660,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"230719f30c1b8a54df3f31778d75802a6507a08b","tid":1128660,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"香港報紙（唔計SCMP）除咗中台之外，幾時開始有人駐外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"細個做留學生賣字試過俾報社叫駐美記者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"間報館咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"唔算無恥<br />\n以前個社會冇咁刻薄<br />\n俾個名你chok CV又好<br />\n都會對你申請各樣文件負責"},{"pid":"ac04f57f7ef96abb5638f2a0e00940bdd1d4ff3e","tid":1128660,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4238b9df3beb811a4beb95307168b25500d1eb","tid":1128660,"uid":51717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"學侵侵咁樣，班市長咁鐘意收容，就係佢哋個市長嘅屋企同班有錢佬豪宅附近起開放式收容所，俾班&ldquo;難民&rdquo;自由出入居住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"依種人咪最勁講風涼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f339de6a23c0c0b065830c282be68ba7d900de97","tid":1128660,"uid":167735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"佢地聯署話收多啲難民就左膠姐，家陣成街都係難民<br />\n佢地無地方住又搞到四圍都亂<br />\n不如比個地方group埋佢地仲易啲管理<br />\n<br />\n乜都話左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a92176a4e07751124ea7246107febeb33bbcb0","tid":1128660,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"咁都左膠？ 好明顯只係越南船民既集中營番板<br />\n你寧願香港而家d 南周圍走定起個集中營？"},{"pid":"392826ee5d6072375af7b29640f6c11da9e5f154","tid":1128660,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"大佬啊，唔該你吔參考下德國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母，收晒啲難民入嚟，搞撚到德國治安幾差有眼睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶劫又強姦乜都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829bea0af576ec93f044053ee2b8347a4f945cc2","tid":1128660,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"392826ee5d6072375af7b29640f6c11da9e5f154","tid":1128660,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"大佬啊，唔該你吔參考下德國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母，收晒啲難民入嚟，搞撚到德國治安幾差有眼睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶劫又強姦乜都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"咁不如我哋先重溫呢條左膠市長過去嘅言論, 再諗下呢個越積越大鑊嘅問題係邊個有大責任去做成:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/3vl9v5a.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fworld%2F3vl9v5a.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=304db035\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/3vl9v5a.html</a><br />\n尊重難民的需求，國家有法律也有責任接待難民，包括安排住宿和相關行政工作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/14/12/22/n4323599.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F14%2F12%2F22%2Fn4323599.htm&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=8f740143\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/14/12/22/n4323599.htm</a><br />\n市長在信中談到，這500名無身份者大多是身體有病或殘疾人士，老人無人照料甚至無法返回原籍國等特殊情況。他們若能獲得正式居留的話，將擁有與法國人同樣的社會補助金等。<br />\n但係<br />\n面對法國近年的經濟危機、財政赤字和失業人口不斷增加的局面，無身份者找工作更是難上難。據統計今年冬天有近3500名無證人員在巴黎地鐵站或街頭過冬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://read01.com/kDoBON.html#.XMWe2-gzaUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FkDoBON.html%23.XMWe2-gzaUk&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b373c57a\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/kDoBON.html#.XMWe2-gzaUk</a><br />\n送多段新聞<br />\n正在中國訪問的巴黎市長伊達爾戈（Anne Hidalgo）5月27日在北京一場媒體見面會上表示，將推動巴黎繼續成為中國遊客高度信任的旅遊目的地，用最好的條件歡迎和接待中國遊客。"},{"pid":"e5324c57ac518ccc10b8a6654987f96b83d87931","tid":1128660,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"駐法國記者<br />\n咁撚揼本"}]}